Titolo: Panzer Dragoon Orta

Anno: 2002

Descrizione: Panzer Dragoon Orta is a 2002 rail shooter game for the Xbox, published by Sega and developed by Sega's Smilebit studio. It is the fourth and final game in the main Panzer Dragoon series. Many of the developers had previously been part of the defunct Sega studio Team Andromeda, which disbanded after the release of the previous Panzer Dragoon game, Panzer Dragoon Saga (1998), on the Saturn. The story follows a teenage girl, Orta, who is rescued from her lifelong prison by a mysterious dragon and must defend herself from the forces of an oppressive empire.

Genere: Rail shooter

Valutazione: 90
